file.name: auth-bearer-flow.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Bearer auth test
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  # - url: https://httpbin.org # live external url
  - url: http://localhost:3231 # will need to mock
paths:
  /get:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ok
security:
  - bearerAuth: []
components:
  securitySchemes:
    bearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
